      protected ModElementGUIEvent(MCreator mcreator, MCreatorTabs.Tab tab, ModElementGUI<?> modElementGUI)

      These events are triggered at different states of a ModElementGUI loading. However, this constructor is never called outside this class.

      Parameters:
      mcreator -

      The MCreator instance where the mod element is.

      tab -

      The MCreatorTabs.Tab that is opened for the ModElementGUI.

      The ModElementGUI that calls each event.
